(** [reduceReverse xs init f]

    Works like {!reduce};except that function [f] is applied to each item of [xs] from the last
    back to the first.

    @example {[
      reduceReverse [|"a";"b";"c";"d"|] "" (^) = "dcba";;
    ]}
*)

